<h2>THE NEST</h2>
<p>The NEST is a practice-based research project in human-AI co-cognition, running as a creative studio, research infrastructure, and externalized memory architecture simultaneously. Director: Dan Sullivan (DPS). The ship is the NEST. The crew is the ship. Four parts of one person working across stations and sessions.</p>
